# Phase 4–8 Follow-up Prompts (Medical Desert Planner)

Paste these one at a time into your CLI coding assistant, in order, only after the
previous phase's checkpoint is green. They assume `AGENTS.md` is in the repo root
and Phases 0–3 are complete. Each prompt re-states the operating rules so the
assistant behaves even in a fresh session.

> Before Phase 4, install the Databricks agent skills (Phase 0.5 in the runbook):
> Claude Code `databricks experimental aitools skills install`, or Cursor
> `/add-plugin databricks-skills`. Check the live menu with `npx skills add
> databricks/databricks-agent-skills --list` — the first-party set is thin today, so
