## Phase 8 — Databricks App (UI) + end-to-end wiring

```
Read AGENTS.md first. We are on Phase 8. Phase 7 is green.

Same operating rules. Build the planner UI in src/app/ (Streamlit or FastAPI) and
wire it as the mdp_app bundle resource in resources/app.yml. The app needs:
  - a district choropleth shaded by desert_score
  - a chat panel routed to the supervisor agent
  - an evidence drawer (source record + claim sentence + confidence + web
    corroboration)
  - an honesty banner (field coverage stats + count of inferred-geography rows)
  - a Save scenario button writing to Lakebase

Run locally first (`uv run src/app/app.py`), then:
  `databricks bundle deploy -t prod`
  `databricks bundle run mdp_app -t prod`
  `databricks apps logs mdp_app`   # if anything misbehaves

CHECKPOINT 8 — the full demo path, reported step by step:
  - App URL loads; map renders; chat returns a ranked district list.
  - Click a district -> candidate facilities show verified-capability badges +
    confidence.
  - Honesty banner shows real coverage numbers.
  - Save scenario -> reload app -> scenario reappears.
  - `databricks apps logs mdp_app` is clean.
STOP and report.
```

